{"id":"api/core/global/ngGetComponent","title":"ng.getComponent","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/global\", \"name\": \"@angular/core/global\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 4, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/global/ngGetComponent\", \"name\": \"ng.getComponent\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core/global\">@angular/core/global</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L26-L79\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts#L26-L79\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"nggetcomponent\">ng.getComponent<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global/ngGetComponent#nggetcomponent\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label global\">global</label>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">檢索與給定 DOM 元素關聯的元件例項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Retrieves the component instance associated with a given DOM element.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n  <div class=\"overload-info\">\n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <span class=\"member-name\">ng.getComponent</span>&lt;T&gt;(element: Element): T | null</code-example>\n\n  \n\n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"引數\">引數</h6>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\">\n        <a id=\"\"></a>\n        <code>element</code>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"param-type\"><code>Element</code></td>\n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n      <p translation-result=\"on\">要從中檢索元件的 DOM 元素。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">DOM element from which the component should be retrieved.</p>\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n  <h6 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"返回值\">返回值</h6>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">與元素關聯的元件例項；如果沒有與之關聯的元件，則為 <code>null</code></p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>T | null</code>: Component instance associated with the element or <code>null</code> if there\nis no component associated with it.</p>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/global/ngGetComponent#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-result=\"on\">給定以下 DOM 結構：</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Given the following DOM structure:</p>\n\n<code-example language=\"html\">\n&lt;my-app&gt;\n  &lt;div&gt;\n    &lt;child-comp&gt;&lt;/child-comp&gt;\n  &lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;/my-app&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">在 <code>&lt;child-comp&gt;</code> 上呼叫 <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">getComponent</a></code> 將返回與此 DOM 元素關聯的 <code>ChildComponent</code>。</p><p translation-result=\"on\">在 <code>&lt;my-app&gt;</code> 上呼叫該函式將返回 <code>MyApp</code> 例項。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Calling <code><a href=\"api/core/global/ngGetComponent\" class=\"code-anchor\">getComponent</a></code> on <code>&lt;child-comp&gt;</code> will return the instance of <code>ChildComponent</code>\nassociated with this DOM element.</p>\n\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Calling the function on <code>&lt;my-app&gt;</code> will return the <code>MyApp</code> instance.</p>\n\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/global\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/global\n - api/core/global/ngGetComponent#nggetcomponent\n - api/core/global/ngGetComponent#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...#L26-L79\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/render3/util/discovery_utils.ts#L26-L79\n-->"}